 Attribute 'type' Metadata:

 

Baseline Model

Destination Model

Notes

The specialised type of an object when the instance object is serialised using a generalised class. For example, a Meter being serialised as an EndDevice in a message exchange should have the type attribute specified as 'Meter'.
